{"tid":1550781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日風向：我地需要大台！","createTime":"2019-09-07T17:37:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T15:05:46.000Z","uid":258696,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cd1d23098d2e44c82dd1e20ad474e676a70328a9","tid":1550781,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:37:54.000Z","msg":"其實我明點解唔敢衝<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1550723\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1550723</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[各有各做??]抗爭已經去到樽頸位啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1550576\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1550576</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自己入去睇，又想推泛民做大台，講到話抗爭會好d，要人帶頭衝。 大台帶頭散水就有，又想同政府進行濕鳩對話，之後運動不了了之<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>無幾耐香港就完全赤化，無得翻身。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外又有人無證無據話大埔爆頭手足死左，講兩句就新聞。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef93a189af50f22b107955ef930483ce3895e906","tid":1550781,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:38:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bfcafa2d8aa27db78bf77d27aa1a0b9e7a9a52ab","tid":1550781,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:39:22.000Z","msg":"下午，美領見。<br />\n<br />\n如果唔想推我p牌仔po就由佢啦，<br />\n<br />\n要講既都講曬。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b84a17f9d538d53f69e18909169898c67418fe1d","tid":1550781,"uid":66221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:49:56.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"25aa7b60e1ee421ec177cc950a660ba549cb0872","tid":1550781,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b84a17f9d538d53f69e18909169898c67418fe1d","tid":1550781,"uid":66221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:49:56.000Z","msg":"推呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:02:46.000Z","msg":"毒撚p牌開post 無人care<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02cbaccb1537cd944b17943fb85be4f356abf252","tid":1550781,"uid":236140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:16:26.000Z","msg":"等緊一個 hit n run 大台！<br />\n<br />\n老老豆豆，直接啲好啲！"},{"pid":"bfa25d4c594fd8c04517990098923174e4757019","tid":1550781,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:03:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"029f60464d4884ed8988fe596afde1e7acdd3567","tid":1550781,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfa25d4c594fd8c04517990098923174e4757019","tid":1550781,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:03:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:05:46.000Z","msg":"Block 左我囉"}]}